'''Tripartite Lines''' was the biggest independent company in the [[Moddell sector/Legends|Moddell sector]]. The company came to prominence during the early years of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. The company's headquarters were located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ovise III]].

